主题: <strong>【安科】让新女儿在某个奇妙的世界冒险吧！</strong><br>
作者: <strong>xiao_shui_guan</strong> 于 <strong>2021-05-27, 周四 20:21:36</strong>
<dd class="postbody">
近日，一款新的vr rpg游戏受到了索拉的同事们的欢迎。这个游戏是卫生纸公司和索大法公司的最新技术的合体产物。<br>现在，已经工作的索拉（这是主角最常用的网名）终于发现，自己曾经最喜欢的桌上角色扮演游戏——居然可以在线上进行vr游玩！<br>所以，在这个周末，索拉终于坐在了电脑前，决定尝试一番最新的信息技术成果。<br>带上了点了下鼠标，索拉进入了建立人物的环节：<br>0-0 建立人物 属性骰点5选1（未分配）<br><span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (5,5,3,2) = 15</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (2,1,2,5) = 10</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (3,5,6,5) = 19</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (4,4,2,3) = 13</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (6,4,2,2) = 14</span>&nbsp; <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (6,2,3,1) = 12</span> <br><span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (3,5,3,6) = 17</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (4,6,4,2) = 16</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (2,5,4,3) = 14</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (3,1,6,3) = 13</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (5,4,1,6) = 16</span>&nbsp; <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (1,5,1,1) = 8</span> <br><span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (5,1,4,3) = 13</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (3,2,4,3) = 12</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (4,2,5,4) = 15</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (6,1,6,3) = 16</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (3,1,4,5) = 13</span>&nbsp; <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (5,5,4,3) = 17</span> <br><span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (6,4,4,1) = 15</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (4,6,2,6) = 18</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (2,6,1,6) = 15</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (3,5,2,5) = 15</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (1,2,2,1) = 6</span>&nbsp; <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (6,5,3,5) = 19</span> <br><span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (3,6,1,2) = 12</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (4,2,3,5) = 14</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (4,2,3,3) = 12</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (1,1,6,2) = 10</span> <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (1,5,1,1) = 8</span>&nbsp; <span class="rolls">投掷 : 4d6 = (2,5,1,3) = 11</span> 
